---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroSection from "../components/index/HeroSection.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
---


<Layout title='Zoar Valley Software' class='bg-dark text-white text-lg'>
    <HeroSection/>

    <Section class="bg-mid py-40 px-20">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-12">What We Offer</h2>

        <div>
            <h3 class="h3">Theme Customization</h3>
            <p>Our theme customization services transform standard WordPress templates into distinctive websites that represent your brand perfectly. We modify existing themes with custom code that adds unique functionality while maintaining performance. Every project includes responsive design implementation for flawless display across all devices, along with careful alignment of colors, typography, and imagery to your brand guidelines. From subtle refinements to comprehensive modifications, we create polished, professional websites that stand out from template-based competitors.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Custom theme modifications and enhancements</li>
                <li>Responsive design implementation</li>
                <li>Brand-aligned visual elements</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </Section>
    
    <Section class="bg-light p-20">
        <div>
            <h3 class="h3">E-Commerce Development</h3>
            <p>
                Our e-commerce development transforms WordPress sites into powerful online stores through expert WooCommerce setup and configuration tailored to your business needs. We seamlessly integrate secure payment gateways that provide your customers with trusted transaction options while ensuring compliance with current standards. Our custom product displays showcase your merchandise with engaging layouts, filtering options, and unique presentation styles that enhance the shopping experience and drive conversions. From single product sites to extensive catalogs, we build e-commerce solutions that balance professional appearance with efficient functionality.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>WooCommerce setup and configuration</li>
                <li>Payment gateway integration</li>
                <li>Custom product displays</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
    </Section>

    <Section class="bg-mid p-20">
        <div>
            <h3 class="h3">Technical Expertise</h3>
            <p>Our technical expertise ensures your WordPress site performs at its best. We implement targeted performance optimizations and speed improvements that reduce page load times and enhance user experience. When plugins clash or create functionality issues, we quickly identify and resolve these conflicts without compromising your site's features. Our database optimization services clean and streamline your WordPress database, removing unnecessary data and improving query efficiency for faster site operation and reduced server load. These technical improvements work together to create a smooth, reliable website that keeps visitors engaged and supports your business goals.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Performance optimization and speed improvements</li>
                <li>Plugin conflicts resolution</li>
                <li>Database optimization</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </Section>

    <Section class="bg-light py-40 px-20">
        <div class="xl:w-1/2">
            <h2 class="h2">Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <p>
                We combine technical excellence with business understanding to deliver websites that perform.  Our team transforms your vision into an engaging digital experience that drives results. 
                Whether you need a complete website redesign, performance optimization, or technical support for your existing WordPress site, we have the skills to help your business thrive online.
            </p>
            
            <p>Contact us today to discuss how we can elevate your web presence.</p>
        </div>
    </Section>
</Layout>
